            <listWit>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet131">BNZ 131: 9 (XIII s.): ff. 88rb-98ra (f. 88r: 20
                  Yakkātit); BNZ "Martyre de Philémon, le ménétrier. ስምዕ፡ ዘፊልሞን፡ መዐንዝር፡ ዘከመ፡ ተከለለ፡
                  በእንተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወዘካልኣን፡ ሰማዕት። Commencement: ወኮነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ፈጸመ፡ ስምዖ፡ አስቅላን፡
                  ባርያኖስ፡ (sic) መኰንን፡ በብሔረ፡ አንጢኖ፤ አዘዘ፡ እምእለ፡ ይቀውሙ፡ ብዙኃነ፡ ይእሐዙ። ወእምድኅረ፡ አኀዝዎሙ፡ አዘዘ፡
                  ያምጽኡ፡ መጻዕርተ፡ ወያንብሩ፡ ቅድመ፡ ምኵናን፡ ወይቤሎሙ፡ ሡዑ፡ … (Rédaction un peu abrégée des Actes
                  grecs publiés dans les "Acta Sanctorum", mart., t. I, p. 895 et suiv. – Comparez
                  ibid., p. 752 et suiv.)"</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient686">BL Or. 686 = BLW 257: 39 (1755-69): ff. 153ra-156ra
                  (f. 153r: 7 Maggābit); BLW "Philemon, ፊልሞን፡ መዓንዝር፡, at አንጢኖ፡ in Egypt, with the
                  reader Apollonius, አጵሎን፡"</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient687">BL Or. 687-688 = BLW 258: 46 (XVIII s.): ff.
                  229va-233vc</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient690">BL Or. 690 = BLW 254: 1 (XV s.) (II parte del ms. BL
                  Or. 689): f. 1ra (acefalo)</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb179">BNA 179: 6 = BNAC 179: 7 = BNACR 163: 7 (1509): ff.
                  32ra-35vc (f. 32ra: 20 Yakkātit)</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1826">EMML 1826: 5 (XIV-XV s.): ff. 50ra-54vb
                  (acefalo)</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML2514">EMML 2514: 28 (1382-88): ff. 137rb-141rb (f. 137r: 20
                  Yakkātit); EMML "Martyrdom of Philemon. For 20 Yakkātit. (Synaxary: 7 Magābit)
                  EMML 1826 (5). ስምዕ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ፊልሞን፡ መዐንዝር፡ … ወኮነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ፈጸመ፡ ስምዖ፡ አስቌላን፡ አርያኖስ፡ መኰንን፡
                  በብሔረ፡ አንጤኖ፡ …";</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML6834"> EMML 6834: 5 (XIV s.): ff. 35rb-40vb (f. 20r: 20
                  Yakkātit)</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML6951">EMML 6951: 30 (XV s.): ff. 154va-158rb (f. 154v: 20
                  Yakkātit)</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/Tanasee122">Ṭānāsee 122 = Dāgā Esṭifānos 11: 4 (XV s.): II: 2: ff.
                  15ra-20rb (f. 15r: 20 Yakkātit).</witness>

